# ISA Ethernet NICs.
#
# DP8390 NIC
#
# ed0: generic driver/EtherEZ98
# ed1: LANEED LD-BDN
# ed2: EGY-98
# ed3: LGY-98
# ed4: ICM-IF-2766/EN-2298-T
# ed5: SIC-98
# ed6: PC-9801-108
# ed7: LA-98
